snippet.description:
Echo in Capistrano is a atmospheric horror game. The game is simple, find the survivors, escape, but most importantly survive. 

Navigate through a giant cavern where the native inhabitants will hunt you down and consume you if you get too close - play smart and use stealth to your advantage. 

@KuzoStudiosPH is an indie solo game developer from the Philippines

